<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4671961>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Phylogenetic tree, chronogram and taxonomic pattern obtained from the matrix constituted by concatenation of COI+NAD2+VAL sequences. The bootstrap (ML)/ posterior probability (BI) supports to the node are given above the node and the time to most recent common ancestor (TMRCA) and the 95% HPD as million years below the node. The results from species delimitation test indicated by a single bar line as all support the same species pattern. Supports to each scenario proposed in BPP species delimitation test shown in dashed box." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4671961/files/figure.png" .

